node.text: Hot off the press: our debut catalog, jam-packed with our need-to-know fall trends. (Link in bio for the digital version.)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joss & Main on August 08, 2021. May be an image of indoor and text.

node.text: It's official! Our debut catalog *just* dropped and it's all inspired by the joy of dressing up again. From fashion trends coming home to exclusive designer picks (@beckiowens), this is an issue you won't want to miss. Tap the link in bio for more.

node.text: Summer-to-fall refresh: We're leaning into a deep color palette, trading in breezy materials for edgier ones, and borrowing some of fashion's best trends. See our story for more, then explore the full trend via our link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joss & Main on August 06, 2021. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text:
A change of seasons means a change of scenery. So for cooler days ahead, we're dialing up the drama of a canopy bed with a metal teardrop pendant, a lush olive green bench, and more. Swipe over to see summer vs. fall.

#jossandmain
#summertofallrefresh
#bedroomideas
#nightstands
#benches
